ood.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2830e0085fc01553cd2d1484731017f67cb868","tid":699961,"uid":62337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"平均一年加幾多人工"},{"pid":"e8816b071f76558dd4a39467683e27b84c23f666","tid":699961,"uid":189703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"400c4e932781fdc98dc45d8357029ec804f80935","tid":699961,"uid":179283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:58:03.000Z","msg":"凍檸茶個茶底點先沖得好飲 同埋用邊隻茶葉?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"應該咁講啦 舊式餐廳既做法有兩款<br />\n都係會叫茶葉嫁啦 <br />\n一隻要自已撈 <br />\n另一隻就叫返黎就現成用得<br />\n當然自已撈會好飲好多+較茶師傳手勢<br />\n撈茶業都要睇手勢 <br />\n所以一杯好飲既茶 唔係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n 茶葉我地叫開捷榮"},{"pid":"b547de01b9705d534e3ab9f0fa21b28c16f872f9","tid":699961,"uid":23937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過做廚房，始終水吧人工低"},{"pid":"063d3272e6e553cfada9a061236ba80561c78127","tid":699961,"uid":189703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e95fd1aa9c5fe73833390d7d027f33d1269c981","tid":699961,"uid":40428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"熱奶茶唔落糖好正<br />\n<br />\n凍奶茶一定要少甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:12:31.000Z","msg":"唔落糖 落鏈奶<br />\n不過肥死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b50214dcecc73c172d5024d6ac5c42f12a81430","tid":699961,"uid":189703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4a2830e0085fc01553cd2d1484731017f67cb868","tid":699961,"uid":62337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"平均一年加幾多人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"人工既野好虛無 <br />\n做得餐廳都唔會點望人工<br />\n係等緊一個時候機會<br />\n去開一間自已既餐廳咁解<br />\n利申：15k"},{"pid":"c1951c33b1969d672ef6d14530c397a56b3736b8","tid":699961,"uid":174670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0